gths against weaknesses is **Candidate\u202fC**. His reliability, quick correct decisions, technical competence, and demonstrated ability to foster a positive crew environment outweigh the communication and development concerns, which are less likely to jeopardize safety on long\u2011distance flights.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fC\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
